headline: 3 Reasons VMC is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Vulcan Materials has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 8%. The stock now trades at $299, marking a 24.2% gain. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.

headline: Building Materials Stocks Q2 Highlights: Vulcan Materials (NYSE:VMC)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at building materials stocks, starting with Vulcan Materials (NYSE:VMC).
